text = "A tactical space combat simulator featuring ship-to-ship combat with realistic damage and weapon systems.

• Ships have armor, shields, and multiple weapon hardpoints
• Weapons have different ranges, damage, and firing rates
• Ships use velocity-based physics
• Tactical positioning and weapon selection matter
• Watch the battle unfold!"

